/2023_07/1688848304-9399.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-07-08T23-29-00-03-00/630_360_1688848304-8260.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_07/1688848304-8260.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-07-08T23-29-00-03-00/630_360_1688848304-1974.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_07/1688848304-1974.jpeg)

