Images: ['[630_360_16878...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/thumb_files/630_360_1687808461-379.jpeg)', '[1688845758-86...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_07/1688845758-866.jpg)']

